Th-Thank you...

00:00:25.590 --> 00:00:27.760
Let go! Let go of me!

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:29.860
Don't touch me in weird places!

00:00:29.860 --> 00:00:31.270
Shut up! Don't say it like that!

00:00:30.090 --> 00:00:31.270
Here's the ticket.

00:00:31.270 --> 00:00:32.800
No! I don't wanna!

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:35.190
I want to go with you guys!

00:00:35.190 --> 00:00:37.150
Little Miss.

00:00:37.150 --> 00:00:42.690
My daughter, who is Jotaro's mother...
Her life is in danger right now.

00:00:44.060 --> 00:00:48.700
We're going on this journey
to save my daughter's life.

00:00:48.700 --> 00:00:52.110
Give up on running away and go back home.

00:00:52.110 --> 00:00:55.080
I'm sure your parents are worried.

00:00:55.820 --> 00:00:56.810
There.

00:00:56.810 --> 00:01:01.410
Fine. I'll make you look good this time, Grandpa.

00:01:05.090 --> 00:01:06.530
What's the matter?

00:01:08.010 --> 00:01:09.010
Nothing.

00:01:10.550 --> 00:01:14.100
See ya! Life is just a bunch of goodbyes!

00:01:17.610 --> 00:01:21.790
But I did sort of want to see
</i>him<i> again before I had to go.

00:01:31.330 --> 00:01:36.140
Bye-bye, Jojo! You better
save your mom, no matter what!

00:01:36.140 --> 00:01:39.010
I'll be cheering you on!

